latestPosts.caption:
Easy ways to make Her happy 🫶🏼⬇️

If you’re looking for max returns - investing in your girl is the best thing. The return is definitely more than 70% 🤪

- flowers ( 250 rs? ) once a week ? 
- a care package during periods ? (500 rs a month? ) 
- pay attention to what she requires. She might just say she likes wearing bracelets, get it for her, she wont always say SHE WANTS SOMETHING. The moment she mentions it, write it down and whenever u have extra $$ to spare ( 1000 rs ? ) just get it for her 
- cook a meal ? Plan dates, theres so much u can do in such little amount. Idk Whats happened to this generation of men 🥴
- write a note before u leave for work 
- handmade cards ?
- try to identify her love language.. 
- u can setup a budget of 2,000 rs per month for her. Consider it a SIP 🤪😂 
And if u do all this & still ur relationship doesnt work; you’re still doing something wrong. Just ask her what she wants. 
Emotional , financial , spiritual , overall wellness is important ☀️
Trust me, this investment will be the best investment of your life ✨🥰 
Effort is all they want 🌸
